Feb 4, 2004 (saw)

The following formulas are set into the "BTA Hall C CONFIGURATION" page
available through the Monticello screen.

Beam Available Condition:

(A>B)&&(!C)
A: HC:selected_bcm.VAL
B: HC:beamok_limit PP NMS
C: HC:abuwait PP NMS


Beam Used Condition
!(A=1||A=4)&&(!B)&&(C=1)
A: PLC_HLC.VAL PP NMS
B: HallCBANU PP NMS
C: HC:exp_ready PP NMS


Experiment Ready Condition
(!(A=1||A=4)&&(!B)&&(C=1))||(C=3)
A: PLC_HLC.VAL PP NMS
B: HallCBANU PP NMS
C: HC:exp_ready PP NMS


Hall Config Change Condition
(A=2)&&(B>-100)
A: HC:exp_ready PP NMS
B: HC:selected_bcm.VAL PP NMS
